he was only fifteen.

85
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,830
Seeing how hard I worked every day,

86
00:06:54,850 --> 00:06:55,530
washing and cooking,

87
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,560
he lied about his age

88
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,430
to join the army at Wangxiang Pass,

89
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,720
just to earn some money

90
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:04,160
so I wouldn't have to work so hard.

91
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,480
He was still so young.

92
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,040
