96
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:21,240
and he even gained a few good brothers.

97
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,600
But it was these very brothers

98
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,920
who in the Death Realm

99
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,780
pushed him out to feed the giant python,

100
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,570
stepping on his corpse

101
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,870
to saved their own lives.

102
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,260
Qin Xuanjiu,

103
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,750
although you weren't there that day,

104
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,390
as an officer,

105
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,480
you let my son meet such an unfortunate end.

106
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,950
