136
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,030
The rune truly is Spirit Spring's tactic.

137
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,790
It's almost dawn.

138
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:51,750
Let's bring her back to the camp first.

139
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,510
Yes, Master.

140
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,200
Su Yishui indeed didn't disappoint me.

141
00:09:58,390 --> 00:09:59,480
