147
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,240
Mr. Qin,

148
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:12,970
Madam Wu's son

149
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,150
was indeed murdered.

150
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,030
Her desire to revenge made her ill-minded,

151
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,270
and caused her to be possessed by an evil spirit.

152
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:18,910
We need to investigate further

153
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,440
to find out what kind of evil spirit it is

154
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,600
that could amplify a person's resentment

155
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,670
