167
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,520
The incident at Wangxiang Pass

168
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:52,940
is related to the root of all evil,

169
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,010
the Spirit Spring.

170
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,030
How do you know this?

171
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,510
Since that time at Mount Absolute,

172
