198
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:42,840
No need for formalities.

199
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,440
Sovereign Su, why brings you here

200
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:48,840
to Wangxiang Pass?

201
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,030
Young Master Yu,

202
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:53,220
