203
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,210
and happened to encounter a demon harming people

204
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,410
at Wangxiang Pass,

205
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:56,030
so we came over.

206
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:56,870
That's perfect.

207
00:11:57,390 --> 00:11:58,600
Our last meeting was brief.

208
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,510
